          <title>Mystics trade 2-time All-Star Ariel Atkins to the Sky for No. 3 pick in WNBA draft</title>
          <description><![CDATA[CHICAGO (AP) — The Washington Mystics accelerated their rebuild, trading two-time All-Star Ariel Atkins to the Chicago Sky for the No. 3 overall pick in this year's draft on Sunday. Washington also received Chicago's second-round pick in 2027 and the rights to swap first-rounders that year.]]></description>
